Let's create a smart enumeration for colors with additional methods and properties:
```csharp
public enum Color
{
    Red = 0,
    Green = 1,
    Blue = 2
}

public static class ColorExtensions
{
    public static string ToHex(this Color color)
    {
        return color switch
        {
            Color.Red => "#FF0000",
            Color.Green => "#00FF00",
            Color.Blue => "#0000FF",
            _ => throw new ArgumentException("Invalid color", nameof(color))
        };
    }

    public static string ToCss(this Color color)
    {
        return $"background-color: {color.ToHex()};";
    }
}
```
